        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(openrouter): guard music generation SSE JSON.parse against malformed frames",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\n`extensions/openrouter/music-generation-provider.ts:128` calls `JSON.parse(data)` on SSE `data:` frames without try/catch. Malformed frame → unhandled SyntaxError → stream crash.\n\n## Changes\n\n- `extensions/openrouter/music-generation-provider.ts`: wrap `JSON.parse(data)` in try/catch → `return false` on failure (skip malformed frame)\n- `extensions/openrouter/music-generation-provider.test.ts`: **v2** — regression test: malformed `data: NOT JSON {{{` frame skipped, valid frame still produces audio track\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Unit test — malformed SSE frame regression\n\n```\npnpm exec vitest run extensions/openrouter/music-generation-provider.test.ts\n\n ✓ skips malformed SSE data frames and processes valid audio frames\n ... (all existing tests pass)\n\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n```\n\n### Fix history\n- v1: source fix only → `unranked krab`\n- **v2**: +regression test showing malformed frame skipped + valid frame succeeds",
